{
  "stem": "3150.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Next-- next in our town, for a while it was like they used to pick everybody up to go to work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, somehow they organized a-- a Judenrat, I think they called them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they used to come in and say, well, we need so many people to go to work, and so many people-- and then had rations.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that probably lasted for about four or five months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By Jewish leadership, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was involved in that for a while, yes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His-- his responsibility was, you know, like to-- not-- not so much as being a policeman, there were [INAUDIBLE] but to-- to deal with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, we-- we had- they set up a-- an office, you know, like it was a lieutenant, and probably like, four, five German to deal with them, and whatever-- whatever came up, you know, whatever they wanted.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So for him to deal with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because my-- my-- in our shtetl, my father was like, you know, the guy that-- he was a businessman.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a-- I know that he can handle problems.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had a lot of respect for him, because he used to socialize with the rabbis.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was given status in-- in the town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can't recall his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He-- he-- he perished in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, food rationing-- you had to.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there was no school at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was really no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First of all, at that-- at that time, which I was almost 11, they-- they even send us to work.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, picking-- picking apples, picking this here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- lined up every day, we went-- we went to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
